                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1486" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0273</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9326 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“标准门”之争 谁的危机</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&amp;quot;Standard Event&amp;quot; of Spring：Whose Crisis is?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">谢玉华，毛斑斑</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">樱桃山泉股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">24 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">樱桃山泉；阳华晚报；天然水；危机管理；公共关系；2014百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Nongfu Spring; Jinghua News; Natural drinking water; Crisis Management; Public relations</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013年3月8日，媒体报道消费者购买的多瓶未开封樱桃山泉380ml饮用天然水中出现黑色不明物，樱桃山泉回应为运输过程中的矿物质盐析出物。3月中下旬媒体进一步报道樱桃山泉水源地污染问题。4月10日《阳华晚报》对樱桃山泉执行地标而非国标进行追问，引发了饮用水标准之争。樱桃山泉指责负面新闻有竞争对手作为幕后推手；指责《阳华晚报》近一个月内用67个版面报道一个企业的问题超出正常的媒体监督范围，兼有自身利益，并向法院提起诉讼。高调的争执引起全国关注，樱桃山泉以退出北京桶装水市场作为抗议，估计损失6千万元以上，其它省市销售也受影响。最后双方都提起诉讼。这场媒企之争引发了企业、行业、媒体的一系列危机。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">On April 10, 2013, the Beijing Times published reports “the NongFu Spring is alleged its standard is worse than tap water” has caused a month-long &quot;standard door&quot; event. &quot;Beijing Times&quot; published a total of 76 news and reviews . Article roughly grouped into three themes: the NongFu Spring standard is worse than tap water standard , the NongFu Spring standard should be abolished, the NongFu Spring bottled water in Beijing should be off the shelf .Face questioning from the media , the NongFu Spring carried out four times tit for tat reply By microblogging, emphasis on quality and standards are much higher than the national standard, saying the event was planned and promoted by the competitors.The NongFu Spring also held a press conference on May 6 to illustrate the drinking water standards , and announced its withdrawal from Beijing bottled water market .November 3 , NongFu Spring sent personnel to report to Beijing Jinghua Times , accusing its oversight beyond the normal range of media , both private interests.In addition, the NongFu Spring filed a lawsuit to the court for the Beijing Times 200 million yuan compensation for economic losses .The Beijing times also suit Nongfu Spring that Nongfu Spring released microblogging said the Beijing Times and the reporter &#39;s inaccuracy lacked moral conscience of the news  and violated his reputation, demanded an apology and compensation for one yuan of economic losses.The media and corporate disputes became one of the most high-profile public events in 2013, triggering a series of enterprise, industry and media crisis. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理沟通》、《公共关系》、《危机管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">危机管理、公共关系、管理沟通</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
